Traits
  Traits are either enacted by staying home and meeting a scenario or cost a certain amount of opportunity to use. Each research team member is allotted three opportunities per Explore Phase.
	Survivor - Passive: does not go MIA when a bigfoot evidence card or two bigfoot tags are revealed, instead lose all but one evidence discovered and gain an eyewitness evidence card.
	Search and Rescue - Stay Home: if another of your research team members would go MIA instead their evidence goes to that location's lost evidence pile and that research team member card is returned to your play area and stays face up. 
	  Turn your Explorer sideways to represent this once per Explore phase use.
	Bush Pilot - 1 opportunity: move to another location's #1 spot. Will have 2 remaining opportunity once their new location board is selected to resolve, play continues to the next research team member card on this location. (even if the location has already been explored this turn)
	Thief - 2 opportunity: select a player on your location that has found evidence, that player shuffles their discovered evidence cards facedown and you take one at random.
	Industrious - they have four opportunities
	Scavenger - 2 opportunity: look through the location's lost evidence pile and place it on this research team member as found evidence.
	Recon - 1 opportunity: look at the top three cards of a location pile and put them back in the same order. Use this only before any research team members are placed during the planning phase
	Intuition - 2 opportunity: look at the top two cards and place one on this research team member and shuffle the other one into the evidence deck.
	Research Expert - Stay home: improve a previously discovered evidence and recieve a plus 2 points card 
	
How to Play

Trading/Negotiating
 
End of Game Scoring

  Laying Claim
In order to Lay Claim you must have a certain amount of evidence in a certain amount of the categories;
Three evidence in Four Categories
Four evidence in Three Categories
Six evidence in Two Categories
All Five Golden Evidence [Auto-win]
